videos.description: Theo John crushes a dunk on a nice pass from Joey Hauser.
videos.headline: Hauser sets up John for slam

videos.description: After Christian David steals the ball, Paul Jorgensen takes it down the court and nails a 3-pointer for Butler.
videos.headline: David steal sets up Jorgensen 3

videos.description: After Markus Howard misses a 3-pointer, Theo John snags the rebound and puts up a dunk to give Marquette a 54-44 lead over Butler.
videos.headline: John widens lead with putback dunk

videos.description: Theo John dribbles around defenders and finds a wide-open Sacar Anim, who rattles off a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Anim sinks deep 3
